hopobject.body: What's the last date I can post this to to arrive in time for Christmas? differin gel 0.3 directions One group for whom this was a disaster was stock pickers, or really anyone who added value chiefly by analyzing a given security or company. What is the point of poring over the books of an Italian dairy company, for example, if the value of its shares was going to be driven more by ECB chief Mario Draghi than by its own products and strategy? For several years the skills that mattered were risk management and the ability to gauge policy-makers' commitment to the status quo.
